# Team Standards

## Pull Request Requirements:

- Every PR must include terraform plan output
- All tests pass (terraform validate, tflint)
- Code formatted (terraform fmt)
- Peer review from another engineer
- Tech lead approval for architectural changes

## Commit Messages:

Follow conventional commits:
- feat: New capability or blueprint
- fix: Bug fix or correction
- docs: Documentation updates
- refactor: Code restructuring
- test: Test additions/updates

## Test Generation:

All new modules require:
- terraform validate tests
- Example configurations in examples/ directory
- README with usage instructions

## Skills Usage:

- style-guide: Blueprint selection, naming, architectural decisions
- code-generation: Adding capabilities from templates
- mcp-discovery: Finding blueprints, fetching files
- security: Secrets management, security groups
